1.00	The_Hidden_(video_game)	The Hidden (video game)	The Hidden is a multiplayer total conversion for the popular Half-Life 2 computer game. The gameplay revolves around the retrieval of an escaped research subject with the twist that the subject is highly agile, incredibly strong and nearly completely invisible. The first beta version was released on June 13, 2005 and their latest release was September 8, 2007.	
